hydrogens and slows down.

653
00:34:25,222 --> 00:34:26,889
Why do we want to
slow the neutrons down

654
00:34:26,889 --> 00:34:28,460
in the first place?

655
00:34:28,460 --> 00:34:31,219
Well, that has to do with
another cross-section,

656
00:34:31,219 --> 00:34:33,219
