660
00:34:46,219 --> 00:34:50,840
sigma fission, the probability,
if a nucleus absorbs

661
00:34:50,840 --> 00:34:53,179
a neutron, that it undergoes
fission and creates

662
00:34:53,179 --> 00:34:57,540
more neutrons and like
200 MeV of recoil energy.

663
00:34:57,540 --> 00:35:01,760
So in this case, I'll
draw it for U235,

664
00:35:01,760 --> 00:35:04,250
